query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(q1 s t1 tq1 u1) NoHashJoin(q1 s t1 tq1 u1 a1) */ select t1.name,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.favorite_count >= 0 AND q1.favorite_count <= 1
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('android-viewpager',
'asp.net-core-2.0',
'common-lisp',
'filesystems',
'hdfs',
'jpanel',
'json.net',
'keyboard-shortcuts',
'label',
'mapreduce',
'sql-update',
'sum',
'uiwebview',
'user-controls',
'webkit')
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow',
'superuser')
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND q1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.upvotes >= 1 AND u1.upvotes <= 100
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND a1.question_id = q1.id group by t1.name;
